{"tid":759921,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"排毒反應？保健產品","createTime":"2018-07-29T05:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T21:33:29.000Z","uid":152052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"260de44caf7484d4bc3e3d75daef5aff086f6a3f","tid":759921,"uid":152052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"唔知係到有冇巴打有食過usana既基本營養素？<br />\n<br />\n前排屋企人買咗d營養素既物體 <br />\n<br />\n咁我本身就身體唔係好健康<br />\n<br />\n成日病 咁之前就同屋企人講過想買維他命食<br />\n<br />\n點知佢就買咗usana既基本營養素<br />\n<br />\n開始食就冇咩野既 係小便個時好黃<br />\n<br />\n但食咗一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就開始嚟料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身體上面生咗好多粒粒 <br />\n<br />\n問返賣比我老母既個條友 佢話排毒反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又話咩好快就會散 但都差不多2、3個星期 <br />\n<br />\n舊既粒粒冇散 新既又起得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打絲打有食過呢個產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇排毒反應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n因為我真係生咗好多粒紅點 ！！<br />\n仲要周不時都好痕！！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係成日開po  又打開5p字<br />\n不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c80ad53b7e408700ec01bb272519584cba702c","tid":759921,"uid":31509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"你老母比人昆啦"},{"pid":"ced2c0999c6ef9f73c39e2dd2ff4b1b07bbdb3c1","tid":759921,"uid":166509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"依d叫好轉反應, 一個月會好"},{"pid":"ad72ccb005565a0efff2b9935943f79125d8dd20","tid":759921,"uid":191391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"好正常既反應<br />\n樓主服用這類長期調理身體類既保健品<br />\n一定要飲夠水 堅持食用<br />\n唔好放縱自己作息飲食<br />\n初初2-3個月既改善會最明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97e11fc9e02d5efdea6e6d9e60ac7ea64e97c43","tid":759921,"uid":152052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced2c0999c6ef9f73c39e2dd2ff4b1b07bbdb3c1","tid":759921,"uid":166509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"依d叫好轉反應, 一個月會好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T21:05:03.000Z","msg":"我今日走左去睇醫生 佢話我係濕疹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心 本身我都有少少濕疹係塊面到 <br />\n<br />\n我亦都深知道有濕疹嘅困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n我已經停左藥2、3日<br />\n<br />\n想睇下停多陣身體會唔會退到d濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59f42d8c40f232d440cba06cee8a13ff3eeec7c","tid":759921,"uid":152052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad72ccb005565a0efff2b9935943f79125d8dd20","tid":759921,"uid":191391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"好正常既反應<br />\n樓主服用這類長期調理身體類既保健品<br />\n一定要飲夠水 堅持食用<br />\n唔好放縱自己作息飲食<br />\n初初2-3個月既改善會最明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,